         <head>Historical Information</head>
         <p>The Depot House Hotel conducted business in Fauquier County
         during the mid-nineteenth century.</p>
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
         <p>Daily register, 1866-1870, of the Depot House Hotel that
         records in chronological order the date customer registered,
         name of customer, place of customer's residence, and room
         number. Register is 558 pages.</p>
